profile:
The Regina Moving Company is dedicated to providing a great moving experience for all our customers. We are local to Regina and specialize in delivering top service to our area, whether you are relocating from or moving into this fine community.

Our Services

We take pride in our local Regina residential moving services—but that’s not all we do. We offer turnkey services for both Residential and Commercial customers, including packing, storage, and long distance moving all across Canada.

Here is a list of the services we offer:

Local moves – We offer safe and convenient local moves in the Regina area for both business and home moving.

Industrial moves – Our relocation services handle industrial equipment safely with the same gentle care we give to personal belongings.

Office moves – One of our most popular services is moving offices quickly, efficiently and safely.

Long distance moves – We go the extra mile, so moves across Canada are no problem—we’ll even move your auto safely.

Relocation – Our turnkey relocation services serve all parts of Canada.

Packing – Proper packing for shipment is one of our specialty services, whether for home packing of personal items or shipment of office furniture and equipment.

Storage – We can provide secure storage for your convenience and the safety of your property before, during, and after a move.

Don’t forget: If you have a special need, we take requests too.

How We Work
We will happily answer any questions you have about your move. We can handle everything in your home or business: books, furniture, glassware, computers, or whatever you need moved!

We wrap each item for protection and take care to ensure that nothing gets broken. All items are delivered to their new location promptly with great respect and gentleness.

We preserve your privacy and strive to provide a stress-free moving experience. We make an extra effort to make sure your valuable belongings arrive safely—it’s what we do.

Contact us by email or phone! We answer emails within 1 business day, and return phone calls within 5 minutes.
